{{Quote|The Rebels' new mag pulse technology was developed by Galactic Electronics in the Corporate Sector. Secretly developing new weapons is bad enough; selling them to enemies of the Empire is treason.|[[Imperial briefing officer]], to [[Maarek Stele/Legends|Maarek Stele]]|<ref name="Star Wars: TIE Fighter">[[Star Wars: TIE Fighter (video game)|''Star Wars: TIE Fighter'']]</ref>}}
'''Galactic Electronics''' was a development firm in the [[Corporate Sector/Legends|Corporate Sector]]. They developed the [[Mag-pulse warhead/Legends|mag pulse]] weapon for the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]], in defiance of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] ban on weapons sales. The Empire retaliated by destroying the company's research station on [[Pondut]].

